{"tid":1448252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚我真係好心酸","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:20.000Z","uid":24888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13b84bcd48e954422e232fa40ef23f868aa2e965","tid":1448252,"uid":24888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"我知大家依家都好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我想同大家講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚所有事都要比全世界知！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今次係一個極好既機會比我地翻盤</span><br />\n<br />\n一直以黎我地都比大人標籤我地搞亂 話我地影響香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係今晚既所有事係個機會</span><br />\n<br />\n比全部人知道個<span style=\"font-size: large;\">真相</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位我地真係要團結</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依幾個月我地做咁多野係為咩！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求又好官警黑又好</span><br />\n<br />\n我地要比全世界知道依啲事<br />\n<br />\n而方法<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係做好所有既訊息傳遞</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武既兄弟 暫時要退一步啊 我地今晚所有人都好心酸啊</span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 你地已經付出好多 等其他人幫你地繼續努力<br />\n<br />\n[<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要爭取返我地原來既香港啊！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bdf73aaef89e48f0f1970162eebde461ad163783","tid":1448252,"uid":282987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣係時候煲大件事啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18736f64c9077c2928d20e12be120825425e0da","tid":1448252,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"而家已經發生咗人道危機 呢個香港已經唔再係香港 大家唔好再諗 要呢個地方係呢個政府底下會好返 冇可能了<br />\n<br />\n好多和理非仲係有一絲希望變返之前咁 社會好返 經濟好返 唔好再傻啦<br />\n穩定返又點 極權政府 黑社會警隊 無限濫權 呢d咁既社會 你甘願屈服 你甘願唔理是非黑白 咩都唔理生活到就算?<br />\n唔好再咁啦 放棄而家既香港 唔需要再諗個經濟會唔會好返 之後點<br />\n如果你仲有良知既話"},{"pid":"b9935af63d97e49e1edf0a8f37e6cd842b137e08","tid":1448252,"uid":24888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好傷心 但係因為咁我地唔能夠就咁就算 醒覺啊香港人！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"9b6e102c112cbaa0063053f3f06d2d413c93ac53","tid":1448252,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"好多人都受傷.&nbsp; 越來越強硬. <br />\n演變成 市民鬥警察. <br />\n轉移視線. <br />\n淡化 送中事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea2de3d7afa99154f499d810fb8d7aeaa43e38","tid":1448252,"uid":24888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"文宣啊各位！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil